column16: Trevor Brown doubles (3) on a line drive to left fielder Matt Joyce.   Gregor Blanco scores.    Conor Gillaspie to 3rd.
Conor Gillaspie singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder John Jaso.   Jarrett Parker scores.    Gregor Blanco to 3rd.
Gregor Blanco singles on a line drive to left fielder Matt Joyce.   Jarrett Parker to 2nd.
Jarrett Parker singles on a ground ball to center fielder Gregory Polanco.   Ramiro Pena scores.
Ramiro Pena triples (1) on a line drive to center fielder Starling Marte.
Brandon Belt strikes out on a foul tip.
Joe Panik grounds out, shortstop Jordy Mercer to first baseman John Jaso.
Denard Span singles on a line drive to right fielder Matt Joyce.   Gregor Blanco scores.

Pirates challenged (tag play), call on the field was overturned: Johnny Cueto grounds into a double play, second baseman Josh Harrison to first baseman John Jaso.   Gregor Blanco to 3rd.    Conor Gillaspie out at 2nd.
Conor Gillaspie singles on a line drive to center fielder Starling Marte.   Gregor Blanco to 2nd.
Jason Heyward singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Gregory Polanco.
Adam Warren called out on strikes.
Albert Almora grounds out, third baseman Jung Ho Kang to first baseman Sean Rodriguez.
Javier Baez pops out to catcher Jacob Stallings in foul territory.
Addison Russell homers (6) on a line drive to left center field.   Anthony Rizzo scores.
Miguel Montero grounds into a double play, first baseman Sean Rodriguez to shortstop Jordy Mercer to pitcher Jorge Rondon.   Anthony Rizzo to 3rd.    Ben Zobrist out at 2nd.
Ben Zobrist reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by second baseman Josh Harrison.   Kris Bryant scores.    Anthony Rizzo to 2nd.
